## Final System Review

The final version was tested using custom PDF files and PNG signature images to evaluate system functionality and integration.

### Upload functionality

PDF upload functionality works correctly.

PNG signature upload also works correctly.

The uploaded files are displayed properly inside the interface and processing starts without issues.

### Signature processing

Background removal functionality is partially working.

Observed behavior during testing:

- Background removal sometimes takes a long time.
- In some cases the background becomes white instead of fully transparent.
- Processing behavior is not always consistent.

Opacity adjustment works correctly.

Rotation functionality works correctly.

Signature resizing functionality works correctly.

Width and height adjustments update the signature size properly.

### Placement system

Placement functionality currently requires improvement.

Auto-detection performs well initially and can identify signature areas correctly.

However, resizing operations sometimes affect final placement quality and positioning becomes inconsistent.

Manual placement currently does not work reliably and requires further improvement.

Observed issue:

- Signature positioning may shift from the intended placement area.

### Frontend evaluation

Frontend functionality works well overall.

Verified functionality:

- Interface loading
- Theme colors
- UI responsiveness
- Loading behavior
- Upload components
- User controls

The interface provides a clear workflow and functionality is organized in a user-friendly structure.

### Export functionality

The final signing workflow operates correctly.

Verified functionality:

- Signature insertion
- Success notification display
- Download button generation
- Signed PDF export

The signed document can be downloaded successfully after processing.

